{"tid":1236551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張國鈞：上周三有人襲警和衝擊　非所有人犯法","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:40:27.000Z","uid":157232,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"737093804bc37e06c83f241151c64dcc95cce072","tid":1236551,"uid":157232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、民建聯立法會議員張國鈞認為，上周三金鐘衝突之中，現場並非所有人也有參與暴力事件，留意到很多年輕人和平表達訴求，又認為學生和青年不是暴徒，希望執法機關小心分辨和處理。<br />\n<br />\n張國鈞表示，當日衝突過程中，有少部分前排人士，參與非法行動，有人襲警和嘗試衝擊立法會，如有證據，應公道處理，但並不代表當日於金鐘和立法會的所有人都犯法。<br />\n<br />\n張國鈞指，不能一籃子概括所有人是暴徒，或者不是暴徒，相信本港法庭也會把關，無理檢控亦不會罪成。"},{"pid":"4a20fffd01e2c2a09468aee88a305202ce6e9214","tid":1236551,"uid":157232,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩 <br />\n民賤聯就專心撞車啦<br />\n依加出曬事先嚟扮好人"},{"pid":"455ee0c483a533cab2b1fb3a302a4d807cd4535c","tid":1236551,"uid":157232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463456-20190617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463456-20190617.htm&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=a277fa9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463456-20190617.htm&h=c8146a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463456-20190617.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c8d5c2642a228baa8222ca76058719fd7c5efeb5","tid":1236551,"uid":5650,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"又割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />割你老母"},{"pid":"bf80c7522de146d54b446294b281d2f24e77401b","tid":1236551,"uid":42090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:37:17.000Z","msg":"為左張選票<br />\n你叫佢講佢老母係男人都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d8